    <summary>Tomighty is a convenient, easy to use, eye candy desktop application that helps you organize and execute your tasks in the Pomodoro™ way.</summary>
    <description>Tomighty is a tool that helps you perform the Pomodoro Technique®. It's intended to be deadly simple, easy to use and unintrusive.

These are the current features:
- Configurable times
- Configurable sounds
- Pomodoro™ counter
- Show time on tray
- Themes
- Multiple languages</description>
